data.name: KGB Kiwi Gourmet Burgers
data.description: KGB is a relaxed cafe style gourmet burger restaurant that serve NZ style gourmet burgers & a NZ style brunch - the shakes & brownie are excellent too. There is also a selection of NZ beers & ciders. We focus on fresh quality ingredients & make all the patties & sauces. We have a wide range of burgers - from Camembert & cranberry, mango jalapeno, to bacon cheeseburgers. We only use NZ grass fed beef & the chicken is free range. The vegetarian patty is walnut lentil & the vegan patty is black bean & cashews. There are 2 Lamb burgers, around 20 bee or chicken & about 15 vegetarian or vegan burger options. There are 4 salads, 4 brownies (caramel, berry, mint & choc) & more.. Cheers :) Ant & Matt @ kgb
